{"tid":199132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【快點XX我？】美女被控強姦的士司機","createTime":"2017-04-13T03:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T09:34:17.000Z","uid":3514,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a551eeedfb998ad907daa631295af6badde9c3","tid":199132,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州一名23歲女子因涉嫌強姦一名的士司機，被拘捕並控以強姦罪。<br />\n<br />\n據報案發於今年1月28日凌晨時分，案中「女主角」卡特（Brittany Carter）與兩名黑人男子召來一輛的士到當地一間酒店接他們。在的士行駛期間，20歲的共犯傑克遜（Corey Jackson）亮刀指嚇司機，然後卡特與他發生性行為。「完事後」疑犯臨走前還從的士司機的口袋搶去32美元，才徒步離去。<br />\n<br />\n29歲男性的士司機後來報警，警方日前拘捕卡特，並以強姦罪和搶劫罪起訴她。早已有涉及毒品案底的卡特現還押監房，同案兩名共犯則仍然在逃。<br />\n<br />\n相係可面，唔益CD rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170412/1/9/4/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-7230651.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170412%2F1%2F9%2F4%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F-7230651.html&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=93f7729c\" target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170412/1/9/4/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F-7230651.html</a>"},{"pid":"360da35b5c846ccf96991e9473701f2ba463756f","tid":199132,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"快點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509e76172ae82af282483b3a6932de4a115c402b","tid":199132,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國俄亥俄州一名23歲女子因涉嫌強姦一名